## Current Deployment

**Location:** Launching from White Plains, NY. Moving to Athens, Greece ~March 11, 2026.

**Athens connectivity:** Flatio booking confirmed through May 15, 2026. Advertised speeds: 195 Mbps down / 19 Mbps up. Dual-WAN failover (wired + Nighthawk 5G) provides redundancy.

**Uptime target:** 99.9% — wired primary + 5G cellular failover + Speedify bonding + battery backup on laptop and router.

**Minimum viable stream:** Laptop + webcam + mic + 10 Mbps upload on ethernet = reliable stream. Everything else raises the ceiling. The stream does not break without the extras.

