## Known Issues & Fix Queue

| Issue | Priority | Fix | Status |
|---|---|---|---|
| No auto-restart when Restream drops VPS connection | **High** | Build shell loop wrapper on VPS | Needed before Athens move (~Mar 11) |
| Keyframe interval ~41s (YouTube health: "Poor") | Medium | Rebuild HoldtLoop.mp4 with `-g 12 -keyint_min 12`, re-upload | Bundle with auto-restart fix |
| Credentials in plain text in internal docs | Medium | Redact from docs, store in password manager | Acknowledged — in progress |
| VPS default root password unchanged | Medium | Change via `passwd` on server | Next SSH session |
| No seamless VPS ↔ OBS handoff | Low | nginx-rtmp traffic controller on server | Deferred — future session |

