## Architecture Decisions Log

| Date | Decision | Reasoning |
|---|---|---|
| Mar 2, 2026 | VPS over OBS-always-on for 24/7 radio | Stream survives laptop downtime. Critical for Athens move and travel. $6/mo. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | 6fps animation speed | 24fps too fast, 12fps still too fast. 6fps matches the lo-fi ambient feel. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | Restream Standard over Free | Free plan has visible branding watermark. Standard ($16/mo) removes it + supports 3 channels. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | Deferred seamless handoff (nginx-rtmp) | VPS is already live and working. Brief YouTube blip acceptable for now. Revisit when live streams are regular. |
| Mar 2, 2026 | Deferred OBS-always-on architecture | Identified as cleaner long-term, but VPS already tested and running. Revisit after Athens setup stabilizes. |

